==French==
===Verb form===
'''protégiez'''

# ''second-person plural indicative imperfect of [[protéger]]'' : Je voulais que vous le protégiez = I wanted you to protect him.
# ''second-person plural subjunctive present of protéger''
[[Category:French verb forms|protegiez]] : Avant, vous protégiez vos élèves = Before, you were protecting your pupils.